title: Japan says a Chinese fisheries patrol boat spotted near Diaoyu Islands
description: Japanese coastguards said Tuesday they spotted a Chinese fisheries patrol boat near the waters of Diaoyu Islands in the East China Sea, Kyodo news reported.
cleanContent: Japanese coastguards said Tuesday they spotted a Chinese fisheries patrol boat near the waters of Diaoyu Islands in the East China Sea, Kyodo news reported.The Chinese fisheries patrol boat was sighted near the main islet in the group of disputed islands, according to a spokesman from the coastguard in Okinawa.																																																																								|  |
